P_1(x) = x
P'_1(x) = 1
P''_1(x) = 0
Q_1(x) = \frac{1}{2}xlog\frac{1+x}{1-x} - 1 
Q'_1(x) = \frac{x}{1-x^2}\frac{1}{2}xlog\frac{1+x}{1-x}
Q''_1(x) = \frac{2}{(x^2 - 1)^2} 
